Package: tabela
Title: Elaborate Tables Existing on Websites
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
  person(
    "Deepak",
    "Bastola",
    email="deepbas99@gmail.com",
    role=c("aut","cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0003-1075-7672"))
Description:  
    Given a root URL, scrape all downloadable files (csv, txt, xlsx, sav, por, RData)
    and optionally any HTML tables.  Returns a tibble of file metadata (name, url,
    rows, cols, etc.) and, if requested, a list of data.frames from table nodes.
